      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power unit paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing performance. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced, maintaining chassis rigidity. Power is sent to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing unparalleled traction and corner-exit stability. The exterior retains its factory luster with perfect panel gaps and zero corrosion, while the suspension remains sharp with OEM+ Bilstein components. A true collector-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
